1
00:01:36,980 --> 00:01:38,000
=Snow Fall=

2
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:40,650
=Snowfall=
=Episode 22=

3
00:01:40,650 --> 00:01:41,940
(This is a work of fiction.)

4
00:01:45,950 --> 00:01:48,950
You can crush those ants
with a snap of your fingers.

5
00:01:50,230 --> 00:01:53,560
Don't you want to seek revenge?

6
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:04,590
(As a human being,
you should cultivate yourself.)

7
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:09,440
(Guide others, and be like water.)

8
00:02:09,880 --> 00:02:12,160
(Even in a bad situation,
act with goodness.)

9
00:02:12,410 --> 00:02:13,740
(Do not hold grievances or blame.)

10
00:02:24,510 --> 00:02:25,320
Mr. Shen,

11
00:02:26,200 --> 00:02:27,230
you're up.

12
00:02:31,440 --> 00:02:32,480
Are you all right?

13
00:02:35,640 --> 00:02:36,480
I'm fine.

14
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:39,710
How long have I been out?

15
00:02:41,270 --> 00:02:42,040
It's been five days.

16
00:02:43,230 --> 00:02:46,230
Did anything happen in Haidong
during these days?

17
00:02:46,710 --> 00:02:47,790
I've saved the newspapers

18
00:02:47,790 --> 00:02:49,160
from the past few days for you.

19
00:02:49,500 --> 00:02:50,530
They're in the study room.

20
00:02:52,550 --> 00:02:53,270
Thank you.

21
00:03:30,380 --> 00:03:37,260
♪Hands that have explored the world♪

22
00:03:38,460 --> 00:03:45,340
♪Other than colors, I have everything♪

23
00:03:47,260 --> 00:03:54,300
♪A night of cold wind and several fates♪

24
00:03:55,700 --> 00:04:02,860
♪I want nothing but you♪

25
00:04:09,320 --> 00:04:10,600
Youwen, it's me. I'm back.

26
00:04:11,320 --> 00:04:12,790
Spread the news about my return

27
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:14,830
and see how people in Haidong react,

28
00:04:15,230 --> 00:04:16,560
including the new Superintendent.

29
00:04:17,640 --> 00:04:19,000
Find out what they're saying.

30
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:22,760
I won't be leaving for now.

31
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:26,470
Since Weilian isn't leaving,
I can't leave either.

32
00:04:28,270 --> 00:04:29,830
All right. Thank you for your hard work.

33
00:04:33,540 --> 00:04:34,240
What's the matter?

34
00:04:36,760 --> 00:04:38,590
We still have a long time ahead of us.

35
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:40,680
A long time?

36
00:04:42,320 --> 00:04:43,030
I mean

37
00:04:44,350 --> 00:04:46,390
we can be together for a long time.

38
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:48,590
Am I right?

39
00:04:52,590 --> 00:04:53,240
Yes.

40
00:04:55,220 --> 00:04:58,180
♪I don't care♪

41
00:04:58,420 --> 00:05:03,260
♪That my sights were deeply affected
by darkness♪

42
00:05:03,780 --> 00:05:05,420
♪When your firm♪

43
00:05:05,420 --> 00:05:08,300
♪And warm arms embrace me♪

44
00:05:08,300 --> 00:05:15,580
♪Become my salvation♪

45
00:05:16,300 --> 00:05:20,180
(Self-Discipline)

46
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:43,800
(If possible,)

47
00:05:45,030 --> 00:05:48,150
(I also wish
to have a much longer time.)

48
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:57,090
(The Economic Development Committee
has been dissolved.)

49
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:58,390
(He's not at home either.)

50
00:05:59,270 --> 00:06:00,830
(Where could Liang go?)

51
00:06:06,830 --> 00:06:08,710
Miss Jin, breakfast is ready.

52
00:06:09,220 --> 00:06:09,910
Prepare the car.

53
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,710
I want to go to the Haidong Army HQ.

54
00:06:12,310 --> 00:06:13,820
But you haven't had your breakfast yet.

55
00:06:13,950 --> 00:06:14,680
I'm not eating.

56
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:43,760
Second Uncle,

57
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:46,910
what's the meaning of visiting

58
00:06:47,200 --> 00:06:48,750
with such a large group of people here?

59
00:06:50,320 --> 00:06:51,240
Jingxue,

60
00:06:52,830 --> 00:06:54,240
I didn't bring these people here

61
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:56,080
for a visit,

62
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:58,390
but to come home.

63
00:07:12,380 --> 00:07:14,380
(Consent for Chairman Change.
Haidong Maritime Industry Association)

64
00:07:14,380 --> 00:07:16,500
(Haidong Maritime Industry Association
Chairman Jin Jingxue passed to Jin Wei)

65
00:07:27,320 --> 00:07:28,800
We're not shipping any opium, right?

66
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:30,030
I guarantee with my life.

67
00:07:30,470 --> 00:07:31,150
Sign it.

68
00:07:33,020 --> 00:07:34,540
(Jin Jingxue)

69
00:07:40,830 --> 00:07:41,910
Did I sign it that day?

70
00:07:44,080 --> 00:07:44,590
Yes.

71
00:07:49,470 --> 00:07:50,710
Even if you set me up,

72
00:07:51,760 --> 00:07:52,830
I indeed have signed

73
00:07:53,470 --> 00:07:54,640
this consent.

74
00:07:57,030 --> 00:07:57,950
I accept it.

75
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:04,200
This is what I like about you.

76
00:08:04,260 --> 00:08:05,890
You take responsibility
for your actions.

77
00:08:08,150 --> 00:08:09,150
After all these years,

78
00:08:09,440 --> 00:08:12,320
you've been living your life as a Jin

79
00:08:12,880 --> 00:08:14,560
while I had to struggle out there.

80
00:08:15,080 --> 00:08:17,120
I don't ask for your compliments.

81
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:21,120
But you kept sending people
to investigate my accounts regularly.

82
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:22,300
Is this an appropriate thing?

83
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:23,830
You're implying

84
00:08:23,830 --> 00:08:25,560
that I'm not competent

85
00:08:27,350 --> 00:08:30,030
and accusing me of dealing with opium.

86
00:08:30,440 --> 00:08:32,230
How can you speak so lightly
of these things?

87
00:08:33,870 --> 00:08:36,400
Jingxue, ask yourself this.

88
00:08:36,470 --> 00:08:38,750
Haven't you hurt my feelings?

89
00:08:39,830 --> 00:08:40,920
I care about kinship.

90
00:08:41,630 --> 00:08:43,280
Everyone in Haidong knows this.

91
00:08:44,160 --> 00:08:45,710
If someone else did such a thing,

92
00:08:46,350 --> 00:08:47,680
they would have been kicked out.

93
00:08:48,710 --> 00:08:49,870
But you're my uncle.

94
00:08:50,230 --> 00:08:51,590
I can't possibly do that.

95
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:55,950
It's my own fault in this matter.
I don't blame anyone else.

96
00:09:03,110 --> 00:09:04,680
Since you want the Jin family so much,

97
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:06,200
you can have it.

98
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:08,470
But I hope

99
00:09:08,950 --> 00:09:09,800
you won't forget

100
00:09:09,800 --> 00:09:11,520
the promise you made to my late father

101
00:09:12,040 --> 00:09:13,680
and don't allow the things you're doing

102
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:15,230
to ruin the foundation

103
00:09:15,590 --> 00:09:17,400
of our Jin family's years of hard work.

104
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:20,870
You don't need to worry
about this anymore.

105
00:09:24,420 --> 00:09:25,400
Please see yourself out.

106
00:09:25,590 --> 00:09:27,110
You just can't wait, huh?

107
00:09:27,920 --> 00:09:28,710
Don't worry.

108
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,710
I'll leave after I pack my belongings.

109
00:10:13,950 --> 00:10:16,160
Mister, do you want
to buy some cigarettes?

110
00:10:17,230 --> 00:10:18,160
Make way, make way.

111
00:10:21,020 --> 00:10:21,940
Cigarettes for sale!

112
00:10:28,800 --> 00:10:30,230
Cigarettes for sale!

113
00:10:34,750 --> 00:10:35,990
Cigarettes!

114
00:11:12,920 --> 00:11:13,590
Miss,

115
00:11:15,560 --> 00:11:16,630
you dropped something.

116
00:11:19,560 --> 00:11:20,350
What's this?

117
00:11:20,800 --> 00:11:21,790
It's the key to my house.

118
00:11:22,160 --> 00:11:22,800
I mean,

119
00:11:25,950 --> 00:11:26,950
the key to your house.

120
00:11:46,160 --> 00:11:47,470
So, are you willing to take me in?

121
00:11:48,560 --> 00:11:49,680
I have nowhere to go.

122
00:11:57,460 --> 00:12:00,540
(Siming Insurance Company)

123
00:12:14,830 --> 00:12:15,800
Have some hot cocoa.

124
00:12:16,110 --> 00:12:17,400
So you'll sleep better at night.

125
00:12:25,230 --> 00:12:26,920
I went to the hospital to look for you.

126
00:12:27,590 --> 00:12:29,080
But they don't know where you live.

127
00:12:30,240 --> 00:12:31,380
Did you go and find me again?

128
00:12:31,520 --> 00:12:33,350
I want to ask you about Liang...

129
00:12:33,350 --> 00:12:34,040
I know.

130
00:12:34,700 --> 00:12:36,010
You're looking for Li Yingliang.

131
00:12:36,520 --> 00:12:37,590
But how can you find

132
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:39,560
Li Yingliang here?

133
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:44,990
Before Liang left the Jin Residence,

134
00:12:45,320 --> 00:12:47,440
he said he would solve
the predicament he was in.

135
00:12:48,320 --> 00:12:49,870
Shen Zhiheng cooperated with his plan,

136
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:50,710
right? Yes.

137
00:12:50,990 --> 00:12:51,560
Yes.

138
00:12:51,750 --> 00:12:52,710
If that's the case,

139
00:12:53,110 --> 00:12:54,990
it means his plan went smoothly.

140
00:12:56,200 --> 00:12:58,320
Why did Chi Shanying suddenly die?

141
00:12:59,280 --> 00:13:00,680
Where did things go wrong?

142
00:13:01,750 --> 00:13:03,350
I did cooperate with Li Yingliang

143
00:13:03,630 --> 00:13:04,680
to find Chi Shanying

144
00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:07,280
and helped him negotiate with Shen.

145
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:10,680
But as for the rest...

146
00:13:16,950 --> 00:13:17,680
I know

147
00:13:18,230 --> 00:13:19,440
you've helped me a great deal

148
00:13:20,210 --> 00:13:21,590
and I shouldn't be questioning you.

149
00:13:28,750 --> 00:13:29,350
I noticed

150
00:13:29,630 --> 00:13:31,990
the department store
outside is still open.

151
00:13:32,500 --> 00:13:33,870
Let me buy
some daily necessities.

152
00:13:34,200 --> 00:13:35,490
It has been a tiring day for you.

153
00:13:35,710 --> 00:13:36,890
You should rest early tonight.

154
00:13:38,080 --> 00:13:39,040
Thank you, Weilian.

155
00:13:52,860 --> 00:13:55,500
(Second Principle)

156
00:14:02,990 --> 00:14:04,520
Can I stop practicing writing now?

157
00:14:04,520 --> 00:14:05,470
No.

158
00:14:05,800 --> 00:14:07,680
If you don't learn to read and write,

159
00:14:07,680 --> 00:14:09,190
people will laugh at you in the future.

160
00:14:09,590 --> 00:14:10,830
But I have you.

161
00:14:11,160 --> 00:14:12,800
We're not the same person.

162
00:14:13,200 --> 00:14:15,230
What I can do will never become
what you can do.

163
00:14:15,750 --> 00:14:16,950
I can overlook many things,

164
00:14:17,680 --> 00:14:19,040
but not your studies.

165
00:14:20,590 --> 00:14:22,080
Then can I write something else?

166
00:14:22,080 --> 00:14:24,050
I don't want to write
the Six Principles anymore.

167
00:14:24,400 --> 00:14:25,680
Then what do you want to write?

168
00:14:28,110 --> 00:14:31,080
Shen Zhiheng.

169
00:14:32,560 --> 00:14:33,230
What?

170
00:14:34,750 --> 00:14:37,830
Zhiheng, Zhiheng. Shen Zhiheng.

171
00:14:42,590 --> 00:14:44,400
What did I do to owe you this?

172
00:14:47,520 --> 00:14:49,920
Heng, I need your help again!

173
00:14:54,160 --> 00:14:56,230
I guess I really owe all of you.

174
00:14:59,400 --> 00:15:00,080
Heng!

175
00:15:01,830 --> 00:15:04,520
I've never been as happy as I am today
in over a hundred years.

176
00:15:04,520 --> 00:15:05,470
Can you feel my joy?

177
00:15:05,470 --> 00:15:06,520
No, I can't.

178
00:15:07,360 --> 00:15:08,830
What's making you so happy?

179
00:15:09,220 --> 00:15:11,140
Jingxue was kicked out of her home
by her uncle.

180
00:15:11,280 --> 00:15:12,230
Now she's homeless

181
00:15:12,230 --> 00:15:13,470
and has moved into my house.

182
00:15:13,470 --> 00:15:16,830
How can you be so happy and laughing
that she's homeless now?

183
00:15:17,320 --> 00:15:18,870
I did not make her homeless.

184
00:15:18,870 --> 00:15:19,440
Heng,

185
00:15:19,830 --> 00:15:21,870
I never had any girls living
in my house.

186
00:15:22,610 --> 00:15:23,860
You're more experienced than me.

187
00:15:23,870 --> 00:15:25,400
What should I prepare for her?

188
00:15:25,400 --> 00:15:27,080
Who has experience? Behave yourself.

189
00:15:28,470 --> 00:15:29,920
I don't know what she likes.

190
00:15:30,230 --> 00:15:31,440
After pursuing her for so long,

191
00:15:31,920 --> 00:15:34,590
how can you not know
her habits and preferences?

192
00:15:35,920 --> 00:15:36,990
This time is different.

193
00:15:36,990 --> 00:15:38,590
Jingxue grew up living a luxurious life.

194
00:15:38,700 --> 00:15:40,070
She's used to using luxury things.

195
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:41,590
The things in my home

196
00:15:41,920 --> 00:15:43,040
definitely won't suit her.

197
00:15:43,920 --> 00:15:47,200
Then whose things would suit her?

198
00:15:52,200 --> 00:15:54,470
Weilian wants money.

199
00:15:56,040 --> 00:15:57,320
I know.

200
00:15:58,950 --> 00:16:00,160
Keep writing.

201
00:16:02,200 --> 00:16:03,560
I'll take you to get the cheque.

202
00:16:04,400 --> 00:16:04,920
All right.

203
00:16:15,600 --> 00:16:17,460
Didn't you say you'd take me
to get the cheque?

204
00:16:19,160 --> 00:16:19,750
Weilian.

205
00:16:22,110 --> 00:16:24,560
When there's an energy transfer
in the Blood Amber Stone,

206
00:16:24,710 --> 00:16:25,920
I will become weaker.

207
00:16:26,470 --> 00:16:28,630
Just like what happened
to your mother before.

208
00:16:30,800 --> 00:16:31,590
Weilian,

209
00:16:33,600 --> 00:16:35,470
please take good care of Mi Lan
in the future.

210
00:17:07,960 --> 00:17:08,670
Liang!

211
00:18:56,240 --> 00:18:57,080
Jingxue,

212
00:18:57,590 --> 00:18:58,520
I'm back.

213
00:19:22,280 --> 00:19:23,590
It seems I've been found out.

214
00:20:08,800 --> 00:20:10,280
Jingxue, why are you running?

215
00:20:13,830 --> 00:20:14,870
Why are you barefoot?

216
00:20:15,390 --> 00:20:15,960
Are you cold?

217
00:20:16,240 --> 00:20:17,800
Here, take my shoes.

218
00:20:20,110 --> 00:20:20,800
Jingxue.

219
00:20:24,240 --> 00:20:26,480
Stop! Stop!

220
00:20:30,800 --> 00:20:31,590
Sir, open the door.

221
00:20:31,710 --> 00:20:32,490
What's your problem?

222
00:20:32,670 --> 00:20:34,240
Please give me a ride.

223
00:20:34,380 --> 00:20:35,870
Where are you going at this late hour?

224
00:20:35,870 --> 00:20:37,180
Anywhere will do. Just be quick.

225
00:20:38,360 --> 00:20:39,830
Mister, sorry about that.

226
00:20:40,320 --> 00:20:41,390
We quarreled.

227
00:20:41,740 --> 00:20:42,560
You can leave now.

228
00:20:42,560 --> 00:20:44,390
What's your problem?

229
00:20:49,560 --> 00:20:50,110
Jingxue,

230
00:20:50,260 --> 00:20:51,110
are you all right?

231
00:20:51,280 --> 00:20:52,320
Did I scare you?

232
00:20:55,830 --> 00:20:57,080
Who on earth are you?

233
00:20:57,430 --> 00:20:58,000
Jingxue.

234
00:20:58,010 --> 00:20:58,800
Don't come near me!

235
00:20:58,960 --> 00:21:00,190
Don't follow me!

236
00:21:03,390 --> 00:21:03,960
Jingxue!

237
00:21:04,110 --> 00:21:05,040
Don't follow me!

238
00:21:29,870 --> 00:21:32,000
Jingxue, your feet are injured.

239
00:21:32,590 --> 00:21:33,110
Let me see.

240
00:21:34,980 --> 00:21:36,560
I told you to stop running away.

241
00:21:36,950 --> 00:21:38,790
I can always find you
no matter where you run.

242
00:21:45,870 --> 00:21:47,240
Who are you

243
00:21:47,240 --> 00:21:48,670
and what are you?

244
00:21:48,960 --> 00:21:50,390
I'm Situ Weilian, you silly brother.

245
00:21:50,390 --> 00:21:51,670
No, you're not!

246
00:21:52,280 --> 00:21:54,240
I have nothing now.

247
00:21:54,240 --> 00:21:55,910
I've lost everything

248
00:21:55,910 --> 00:21:58,080
and even you're picking on me.

249
00:21:58,520 --> 00:22:01,080
What have I done wrong?

250
00:22:01,520 --> 00:22:04,240
What did I do wrong?

251
00:22:04,800 --> 00:22:05,800
I swear

252
00:22:05,800 --> 00:22:07,280
I will never hurt you.

253
00:22:36,060 --> 00:22:37,820
Jingxue, come and have breakfast.

254
00:22:51,640 --> 00:22:52,640
I told you

255
00:22:52,640 --> 00:22:53,960
I won't do anything to you.

256
00:22:55,920 --> 00:22:56,960
Then tell me.

257
00:22:57,960 --> 00:22:59,160
What on earth are you?

258
00:23:00,070 --> 00:23:00,790
I don't know.

259
00:23:01,200 --> 00:23:02,640
When my mother gave birth to me,

260
00:23:02,920 --> 00:23:04,070
I was already like this.

261
00:23:05,160 --> 00:23:06,270
I need blood to survive.

262
00:23:06,840 --> 00:23:08,750
I'm also stronger than humans.

263
00:23:09,030 --> 00:23:10,310
Back when you were at my house,

264
00:23:11,070 --> 00:23:12,510
you had been lying to me.

265
00:23:13,030 --> 00:23:14,160
You can't say that, Jingxue.

266
00:23:14,750 --> 00:23:17,270
My feelings for you are real.

267
00:23:20,030 --> 00:23:21,360
Then did you lie to me

268
00:23:22,960 --> 00:23:24,070
about Liang?

269
00:23:27,200 --> 00:23:28,310
Would you believe me

270
00:23:28,880 --> 00:23:29,640
if I said I didn't?

271
00:23:31,180 --> 00:23:33,860
You're a liar! Liar! Liar!

272
00:23:33,860 --> 00:23:36,400
You lied to me!

273
00:23:42,290 --> 00:23:43,190
Not hitting me anymore?

274
00:23:50,670 --> 00:23:52,760
Calm down and have your breakfast first.

275
00:23:53,020 --> 00:23:55,580
We still have a long time ahead of us.

276
00:24:00,960 --> 00:24:03,150
(He must know Liang's whereabouts.)

277
00:24:03,830 --> 00:24:05,080
( He definitely knows.)

278
00:24:18,150 --> 00:24:19,080
Eat up.

279
00:24:25,760 --> 00:24:26,670
You're right.

280
00:24:27,210 --> 00:24:28,400
I accept what's happening now.

281
