the new superintendent

285
00:24:52,800 --> 00:24:53,670
and nothing else?

286
00:24:53,670 --> 00:24:54,150
Yes.

287
00:24:54,630 --> 00:24:56,430
You haven't returned that day.

288
00:24:56,520 --> 00:24:58,680
