So he specifically sent someone
to the press office

292
00:25:07,790 --> 00:25:09,190
to ask me to bring the invitation over.

293
00:25:16,430 --> 00:25:17,350
It's a Hongmen Feast.

294
00:25:19,720 --> 00:25:21,080
I'm surprised you know about it.

295
00:25:22,040 --> 00:25:22,870
Don't go.

296
00:25:24,350 --> 00:25:26,590
Wu Zhongyi is different
from Chi Shanying.

297
00:25:26,590 --> 00:25:27,990
He is trying to extend an olive branch.

298
00:25:28,480 --> 00:25:28,960
Really?

299
00:25:28,970 --> 00:25:30,890
He gave the invitation
through the press office.

300
00:25:31,560 --> 00:25:34,080
So he's publicizing the matter.

301
00:25:34,310 --> 00:25:36,660
If something happens to me,
he won't escape responsibility.

302
00:25:36,910 --> 00:25:39,350
Doesn't this seem like
he's trying to make amends?

303
00:25:40,350 --> 00:25:41,390
Does that mean

304
00:25:41,720 --> 00:25:43,280
we don't have to leave Haidong anymore?

305
00:25:46,350 --> 00:25:47,800
After the feast,

306
00:25:48,320 --> 00:25:49,480
I'll take you out for a walk.

307
00:25:55,660 --> 00:25:59,220
(Siming Insurance Company)

308
00:26:11,910 --> 00:26:13,400
I like the clothes

309
00:26:15,040 --> 00:26:15,910
you bought for me.

