320
00:27:02,200 --> 00:27:03,040
That's not the same.

321
00:27:07,590 --> 00:27:08,590
Drink this wine.

322
00:27:12,670 --> 00:27:14,630
Are you afraid I've poisoned this wine?

323
00:27:19,080 --> 00:27:19,960
