324
00:27:20,430 --> 00:27:21,280
or you'll fall.

325
00:27:22,080 --> 00:27:23,390
That movie was great.

326
00:27:24,590 --> 00:27:25,480
What about the food?

327
00:27:25,600 --> 00:27:26,350
They're delicious.

328
00:27:27,560 --> 00:27:28,480
Which one is delicious?

329
00:27:29,700 --> 00:27:30,870
The sausage tasted delicious.

330
00:27:32,110 --> 00:27:32,910
Mi Lan,

331
00:27:33,620 --> 00:27:34,890
