360
00:29:18,480 --> 00:29:19,430
Then where is he?

361
00:29:22,430 --> 00:29:23,320
I don't know.

362
00:29:25,600 --> 00:29:26,720
You're still not telling me.

363
00:29:27,910 --> 00:29:29,870
